Ɔpɔstɔlɔ Joani akafunde ate : “ Onto lahalange ɔnango lɛnande hakoke nanga Nzambi lahandɛnyi . ”
Ɛnya anangɛso l’akadiyɛso ngandji kawaokayɛ ( Enda odingɔ 17 )
