b ) Wetshelo akɔna w’ohomba wakakondja ɔnangɛso la la Thaïlande lo dikambo di’olimu ande ?
Etombelo waki la dui sɔ ele , l’ɔtɛ w’olimu akɔ dimi komongaka la wenya efula wa nsala akambo wa lo nyuma .
L’ekomelo , lakayoshihodia ɔnɛ dia mbetsha wahɔ wa Diolelo lo dihole dia ntondo , dimi pombaka nkamba olimu okina . ”
Nde mbutaka ate : “ L’ɔkɔngɔ wa dimi ndjakongɛ l’edja k’ɔnɔnyi w’otondo , lakɔshi yɛdikɔ ya sondjaka krɛmɛ lo shinga .
L’etatelo , laki l’ekakatanu wendana l’ekondjelo ndo lakakɔmɔ .
Etena kakamahomana l’asekami wa l’olimu wa ntondo , vɔ wakambɔlɛ ndo wakamimbola lande na kakamɛnyi ɔnɛ nsondja krɛmɛ ndeka olimu wa nɔngɔsɔla ɔrdinatɛrɛ , lɛnɛ ele ndo mashinyi washa tshitshi dimɛna .
Lakalɔmbɛ Jehowa dia nde kimanyiyami dia ntondoya ndo dia nkotsha oyango ami wa monga la wenya efula wa ndjasha l’elimu wa lo nyuma .
Lakayeya kɛnɛ kakalangaka waa kidiya yami dimɛna ndo lakayonga la diewo dia nsala krɛmɛ .
Kombeta edja , wakasombaka krɛmɛ tshɛ yakamasalaka lushi la lushi .
Ɛlɔ kɛnɛ , laya l’ekondjelo ka dimɛna efula ndeka etena kakamakambaka olimu wa nɔngɔsɔla ɔrdinatɛrɛ .
Vɔ wamboleka mbishami ɔngɛnɔngɛnɔ nɛ dia dimi bu la lonyangu ndo l’ekiyanu oko wakimi la wɔ l’olimu ami wa ntondo .
Ndo dui dioleki ohomba ele , lamboleka ndjaoka suke la Jehowa . ” ​ — Adia Mateo 5 : 3 , 6 .
L’ɔkɔngɔ wa nde nongola batisimu , nde akate ate : “ Dikambo ɔtɔi dianyangami ele , lakashisha wenya efula la ntondo ka dimi nshihodia ɔnɛ kambɛ Jehowa mbishaka ɔngɛnɔngɛnɔ w’efula ndeka oweso wa tɔkɛnyɔ ta l’andja ɔnɛ . ”
Yeso akate ɔnɛ : “ Ndooko onto lakoka kambɛ ewandji 2 olimu . ”
Nde akakotsha ate : “ Nyu hanyokoke kambɛ Nzambi la ɛngɔnyi olimu oko ɛhɔmbɔ . ”
( Adia 1 Kɔrɛtɔ 2 : 14 . )
Enda sawo diele l’ɔtɛ a dui ɔnɛ : “ Onde tɔkɛnyɔ takɛnyayɛ tekɔ amɛna ? ”
Ndo nto , takasambishaka mbala la mbala . ”
Taki la lonyangu dia ntshika ambeki aso wa Bible . ”
Koko ngɔndɔ ɔtɔi oma laasɔ , vɔ wakalongola losango la dimɛna efula .
Miriam mbutaka ate : “ Wakatotɛ dia nkamba oko ambatshi mboka wa laande .
Ande ɔngɛnɔngɛnɔ waki la so dia ntshikala lɛnɛ akiso lee ! ”
Vɔ wamboyaɛkɛ lo daka diele lo Osambo 37 : 5 , diata ɔnɛ : “ Kimɔ mboka kayɛ le Jehowa ; yaɛkɛ le nde , ko nde ayosala akambo lo wahɔ ayɛ . ”
Ɛlɔ kɛnɛ , tekɔ la lɔsɛnɔ l’ɔsɛlɛngɛ ndo hatohombe ndooko ɛngɔ k’ohomba . ”
Lande na kakokaso nongamɛ dia lɔsɛnɔ la lo diwala ndo nkumbo layonga l’asui amɔtshi ?
Sho koka monga l’eshikikelo ɔnɛ nde nangaka kɛnɛ koleki ɔlɔlɔ le so oko wakidiɔ le ekambi ande wa lo nshi y’edjedja . ​ — Adia Jɛrɛmiya 29 : 11 , 12 .
( Adia 1 Samuɛlɛ 1 : 4 - 7 . )
Paula mbutaka ate : “ Kaanga mbaki Ann kombotɔka la mi , woho wakandayasha le mi la ngandji tshɛ , akakimanyiya efula .
Dui sɔ diakakimanyiya dia ntetemala kambɛ Jehowa . ”
( Adia Osambo 145 : 18 , 19 . )
“ Lɛnɛ ele ɛngɔ kayɛ ka nɛmɔ , lɛkɔ mbayoyala ndo otema ayɛ . ” ​ — LUKA 12 : 34 .
