“ Tanyowanake lo mboka . ”
“ Sangwelo ndanaka lam’aha ɔkɛtshanyelo . ”
Michael mbutaka ate : “ Ɔnalengo akadimanyiya l’otema ɔtɔi . ”
“ Nyotetemale mbikikanɛ kɔlɔ ndo nyodimanyiyanake l’otema ɔtɔi lam’asanyu , oyadi kaanga onto ekɔ la dikambo dia nyangɛ osekande . ”
Ɛlɔ kɛnɛ , vɔ wokana dimɛna ndo wosambisha lokumu l’ɔlɔlɔ .
Koko , woho weso la lonto lotshikitanyi koka nto tokonya diaha mbɔtɔnɛ lo tokanyi ndo l’ewanu .
Lam’ele nkɛlɛ kakatadɛka , lakatshike tɛkɛtshanya la nde .
Lakate nte : ‘ Nde hanɛmiya woho wahombama , laasɔ ndo dimi haawɔlɛmiya . ’ ”
Nde mbutaka ate : “ Lakatatɛ nshihodia dia dimi mbakasale kɔlɔ ndo lakanyange efula .
Lakashihodia dia dimi pombaka ntshikitanya kanyi yami .
L’ɔkɔngɔ wa nɔmba Jehowa lo dikambo diakɔ , lakatɔlɛ kadiyɛso kakɔ woshasha ɔmɔtshi wa tshitshɛ ndo lakofundɛ nɔtɛ dia mbɔlɔmba edimanyielo l’ɔtɛ wa dionga diami dia kɔlɔ .
Takakumbatanɛ ndo takɔshi yɛdikɔ ya mbohɛ dui sɔ .
Taya bu ndooko l’okakatanu nto . ”
